cff-version: 1.2.0
type: software
title: "Text Clustering as Classification with LLMs (PPD M2 MLSD Reproduction)"
message: "If you use this software, please cite it using the metadata from this file."
abstract: |
  A comprehensive reproduction and extension of the paper "Text Clustering as
  Classification with LLMs" with novel pipelines including SEAL-Clust, Hybrid
  Clustering, and Graph Community Clustering. Includes full experimental results,
  baselines, and reproducible analysis.

